<h1 id="private-email-addresses">Private email addresses</h1>

<a id="tails-support-private"></a>

<h2 id="tails-support-private">tails-support-private</h2>

You can write encrypted emails to <tails-support-private@boum.org> if
you need help in private.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-bugs.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#support]]).

[[!inline pages="support/talk/languages.inline" raw="yes" sort="age"]]

<h2 id="tails-press">tails-press</h2>

If you are a journalist and want to write about Tails, or if you want to
send us links to [[press articles|press]] about Tails, write to
<tails-press@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-press.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#press]]).

<h2 id="tails-accounting">tails-accounting</h2>

If you want to contact our accounting team, write to <tails-accounting@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-accounting.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#accounting]]).

<h2 id="tails-fundraising">tails-fundraising</h2>

If you want to contact our fundraising team, write to <tails-fundraising@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-fundraising.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#fundraising]]).

<h2 id="tails-foundations">tails-foundations</h2>

To get in touch with the Tails [[Foundations
Team|contribute/working_together/roles/foundations_team]], write to
<tails-foundations@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-foundations.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#foundations]]).

<h2 id="tails-mirrors">tails-mirrors</h2>

If you want to operate a Tails mirror, see [[contribute/how/mirror]].

To get in touch with the team that manages our pool of mirror,
write to <tails-mirrors@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-mirrors.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#mirrors]]).

<h2 id="tails-sysadmins">tails-sysadmins</h2>

To talk about our infrastructure (servers, test suite, repositories,
mirrors, etc.), write to <tails-sysadmins@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-sysadmins.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#sysadmins]]).

<h2 id="tails-weblate">tails-weblate</h2>

To talk about the [[Tails translation platform|contribute/how/translate/with_translation_platform]], write to <tails-weblate@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-weblate.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#weblate]]).

<h2 id="board">tails-board</h2>

You can write to the Board at <tails-board@boum.org> about sponsorship requests
and governance issues.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-board.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#board]]).

<h2 id="tails">tails</h2>

For matters that are listed in none of the above and for
vulnerabilities disclosures, you can write encrypted emails to
<tails@boum.org>.

[[OpenPGP key|tails-email.key]]
([[details|doc/about/openpgp_keys#private]]).

<h1 id="chat">Chat rooms</h1>

You can join our [[users chat room|support/chat]] and
[[developers chat room|contribute/chat]]. Only a few Tails
developers hang out there, so email is preferred for anything that
might be of interest for the larger community.
